006package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model.constraint;
007
008import java.util.List;
009
010import edu.umd.cs.findbugs.annotations.NonNull;
011
012public interface IFeatureModelConstrained extends IModelConstrained, IFeatureValueConstrained {
013  @Override
014  IModelConstrained getConstraintSupport();
015
016  @Override
017  default List<? extends IIndexConstraint> getIndexConstraints() {
018    return getConstraintSupport().getIndexConstraints();
019  }
020
021  @Override
022  default List<? extends IUniqueConstraint> getUniqueConstraints() {
023    return getConstraintSupport().getUniqueConstraints();
024  }
025
026  @Override
027  default List<? extends ICardinalityConstraint> getHasCardinalityConstraints() {
028    return getConstraintSupport().getHasCardinalityConstraints();
029  }
030
031  @Override
032  default void addConstraint(@NonNull IIndexConstraint constraint) {
033    getConstraintSupport().addConstraint(constraint);
034  }
035
036  @Override
037  default void addConstraint(@NonNull IUniqueConstraint constraint) {
038    getConstraintSupport().addConstraint(constraint);
039  }
040
041  @Override
042  default void addConstraint(@NonNull ICardinalityConstraint constraint) {
043    getConstraintSupport().addConstraint(constraint);
044  }
045}
